title: BRIEF-United Overseas Australia Says FY ‍Net Profit Attributable $109.1 Mln, Down 32.54 Pct ​

organizations.name: brief-united overseas australia says fy ‍net profit attributable

text:
Feb 27 (Reuters) - United Overseas Australia Ltd:
* ‍DECLARED A FINAL DIVIDEND (UNFRANKED) OF 2.5 CENTS PER SHARE​
* ‍FY REVENUES FROM ORDINARY ACTIVITIES $328.8 MILLION, UP 1.45%
* FY ‍NET PROFIT ATTRIBUTABLE TO MEMBERS DOWN 32.54 PERCENT TO $109.1 MILLION​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
